{"tid":1602042,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"有個文宣小建議","createTime":"2019-09-29T09:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T09:33:21.000Z","uid":273948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"064165fbe64006711b9494c434532a2df9281a98","tid":1602042,"uid":273948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:30:39.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇生果報 見到有一個好靚嘅日曆 記錄由六月至八月抗爭運動每個時刻 個出設好清晰 好幫到我重溫舊夢 <span style=\"color: red;\">提醒我點解要堅持</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹不才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只係有個建議 想有電子版嘅日程表( or google calendar/ RSS feed嗰啲)<br />\nclick入去會有當日發現嘅事情 可以包括時地人事 被捕 等等<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭集會</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲集會</span><br />\n義士消息<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">外國活動or消息</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">共國消息</span><br />\n<br />\n將呢啲事件用schedule方式去表達 將抗爭變成生活一部份 唔想香港人咁善忘<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c941e8161a18a1a9b54ccca2f7d205c0f217309","tid":1602042,"uid":273948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"P牌冇得 pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d88cc9e1e29d9e4dfb6c8a22dfed247f7a9f6aa","tid":1602042,"uid":273948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7a254ce703daaace894a86cf873ee322152a30","tid":1602042,"uid":269301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"731af4a242dbf45b4218fc4c5b7f4155f3c655fb","tid":1602042,"uid":269301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T09:32:39.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"b6058e23addcedbea217d